               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17671209-2-off6-c34" targOrder="Y" targets="t17671209-2-defend35 t17671209-2-off6 t17671209-2-verdict9"></join>
         
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="176712090003"></xptr>2. (L.) 
               <persName id="t17671209-2-defend35" type="defendantName">
                  Anthony 
                  Green 
               <interp inst="t17671209-2-defend35" type="surname" value="Green"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-2-defend35" type="given" value="Anthony"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-2-defend35" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was indicted for <rs id="t17671209-2-off6" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17671209-2-off6" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-2-off6" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a silk handkerchief, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17671209-2-victim37" type="victimName">
                     Ephraim 
                     Muller 
                  <interp inst="t17671209-2-victim37" type="surname" value="Muller"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-2-victim37" type="given" value="Ephraim"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-2-victim37" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17671209-2-off6 t17671209-2-victim37"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17671209-2-cd7" type="crimeDate">Dec. 1</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17671209-2-off6 t17671209-2-cd7"></join>. ++</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17671209-2-person38">
                  Ephraim 
                  Muller 
               <interp inst="t17671209-2-person38" type="surname" value="Muller"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-2-person38" type="given" value="Ephraim"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17671209-2-person38" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 1st of December I was near the corner of <placeName id="t17671209-2-crimeloc8">Rood-lane in Fenchurch-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17671209-2-crimeloc8" type="placeName" value="Rood-lane in Fenchurch-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17671209-2-crimeloc8" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17671209-2-off6 t17671209-2-crimeloc8"></join>, the prisoner ran between me and the wall; I felt him take something from my pocket; I turned round, and saw my handkerchief in his hand; I took it from him, and delivered him in charge of a constable.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence.</p>
               <p>I was coming from work, I saw the handkerchief lying, I took it up to look at it; the gentleman turned round, and said, you have picked my pocket; my father keeps a peter-boat, and I work at a rope-ground.</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. There was not time enough for the prisoner to stoop to take it up, between the time of his passing me and my seeing it in his hand.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17671209-2-verdict9" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17671209-2-verdict9" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>. <rs id="t17671209-2-punish10" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17671209-2-punish10" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17671209-2-defend35 t17671209-2-punish10"></join>
               T
            </rs>.</p>
